\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Tier~1 safety evaluation. \textbf  {Left:} Safety degradation trajectories in the RtA--Toxicity plane under escalating adversarial attacks: No Jailbreak ($\circ $), Single-turn ($\square $), and Multi-turn ($\triangle $). The safe region lies in the top-left (high RtA, low Toxicity). Dashed/solid lines denote text/audio modalities; red/blue distinguish reasoning (Thinking/Pro) and standard variants. \textbf  {Right:} Agentic Refusal-to-Answer (RtA) under Direct vs.\ Indirect harm (a), and the text--audio vulnerability gap in Direct harm mirroring single-turn jailbreak behavior (b).}}{4}{figure.caption.5}\protected@file@percent }
